			<description><![CDATA[<p><font size="4">I. Overview</font><br /><br />The Common Public License (CPL) is published by IBM. It is a free/open source software license approved by the Open Source Initiative (OSI) and the Free Software Foundation (FSF). The aim of the CPL is to encourage and support collaborative open source development.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>]]></description>
			<author>contact@openfoundry.org (賴嘉倫 Ciia Lun Lai)</author>
